      "body" : "<code>if(JavaVersion.current() != JavaVersion.VERSION_1_8) throw new GradleException(&quot;This project requires Java 8, but it&#39;s running on &quot;+JavaVersion.current())</code> This is how I sort this issue out, right in the beginning of the build.gradle file."
